      * T32-DEAL-OBO -- VERIFY OFF-BY-ONE IN HIT PATH (CALC-3)
      * STORY 3.2: HIT CARD STORED AT SLOT N NOT N+1
       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. T32-DEAL-OBO.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
           COPY WS-DECK.
           COPY WS-HANDS.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-1.
           DISPLAY "=== T32: OFF-BY-ONE DEAL VERIFICATION ==="
           MOVE ZEROS TO WS-DK
           MOVE ZEROS TO WS-HND
           CALL 'BJACK-DECK' USING BY REFERENCE WS-DK
           CALL 'BJACK-DEAL' USING BY REFERENCE WS-DK WS-HND
           DISPLAY "INITIAL DEAL (WS-PC=0 ON ENTRY):"
           DISPLAY "  WS-PC   = " WS-PC " (EXPECTED 2)"
           DISPLAY "  SLOT 1: " WS-PRK(1) " FV=" WS-PFV(1)
           DISPLAY "  SLOT 2: " WS-PRK(2) " FV=" WS-PFV(2)
           DISPLAY " "
           DISPLAY "HIT (WS-PC=2 ON ENTRY TO BJACK-DEAL):"
           CALL 'BJACK-DEAL' USING BY REFERENCE WS-DK WS-HND
           DISPLAY "  WS-PC   = " WS-PC " (EXPECTED 3)"
           DISPLAY "  SLOT 1: " WS-PRK(1) " FV=" WS-PFV(1)
               " (UNCHANGED)"
           DISPLAY "  SLOT 2: " WS-PRK(2) " FV=" WS-PFV(2)
               " (BUG: HIT CARD OVERWROTE SLOT 2)"
           DISPLAY "  SLOT 3: " WS-PRK(3) " FV=" WS-PFV(3)
               " (BLANK: CORRECT SLOT NEVER WRITTEN)"
           DISPLAY " "
           DISPLAY "CORRECT: HIT CARD IN SLOT 3, SLOT 2 UNCHANGED"
           STOP RUN.
